de.oaam.model.oaam.library

Interface TaskOutputTrigger

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, OaamBaseElementA
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TaskOutputTriggerImpl

    public interface TaskOutputTrigger
extends OaamBaseElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Task Output Trigger'. The trigger condition for the output. If the trigger condition is true, the output is calculated. A trigger is either a Boolean combination of available inputs or a fixed rate.

    The following features are supported:

    • Logic
    • Fixed Rate
    • Is Fixed Rate
    See Also:
    LibraryPackage.getTaskOutputTrigger()

      • isIsFixedRate

        boolean isIsFixedRate()
        Returns the value of the 'Is Fixed Rate' attribute. The default value is "false". If true the output is calculated at a fixed rate and the fixedRate attribute must be set. If false, the output is calculated if a certain combinations of inputs is available. In the latter case logics must be set.
        Returns:
        the value of the 'Is Fixed Rate' attribute.
        See Also:
        setIsFixedRate(boolean), LibraryPackage.getTaskOutputTrigger_IsFixedRate()
